{"tid":683144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【太子珠寶劫案】疑犯何東成為十大重犯 曾械劫珠寶1.2億被判17次終身監禁","createTime":"2018-05-29T12:38:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T04:37:25.000Z","uid":33028,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"6fbc0103c5110299599b15c41a17d88f73e45bb7","tid":683144,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:38:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180529/58252396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F58252396&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=60100732\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F58252396&h=e77ca45e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180529/58252396</a><br />\n尖沙嘴海港城太子珠寶，上周三(23日)發生劫案，遭兩名持刀賊人掠去500萬元珠寶首飾( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ILYNHC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ILYNHC&d=YPAu4AnCEAaVi65pa0N96Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ec8423ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2ILYNHC</a> )。警方拘捕一名60歲男子涉嫌與案有關。消息稱，被捕的60歲疑犯為何東成，《蘋果》翻查資料，發現他因械劫被判十七次終身監禁，被喻為本港開埠以來最危險的械劫集團首腦。他並曾因涉嫌謀殺被控，但最終只是誤殺罪，判監25年。<br />\n<br />\n他曾於1986至1991年率領一群悍匪做案19次，掠去港九新界18間珠寶金行1.2億元，更有市民被槍殺及槍擊至終身癱瘓。當時他與其黨羽落網後，93年被控20多項罪名，其中17項打劫及開槍拒捕罪，均判終身監禁，期後他獲覆核刑期，年前出獄，未料最終又再犯打劫珠寶行。"},{"pid":"03b03054a7621b64caa7f914a75693431c43b487","tid":683144,"uid":82917,"like":165,"dislike":9,"score":156,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"我地何東姊妹。。。"},{"pid":"3957464fea0fc5d26873a8efb5f5bb3837de77df","tid":683144,"uid":102096,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f30f8da3405b80222828192c7c40bea265e093e4","tid":683144,"uid":8014,"like":122,"dislike":6,"score":116,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"今時今日純粹靠電話都呃到幾球<img src=\"/as